   Script `scripts/e2e-demo.sh` executes full journey (create DID → mock attestation → upload to IPFS → register on contract → verify authorship) in under 5 minutes, outputs saved to `demo-output.log`

3. **Public Demo:**  
   Live frontend at public URL (no login required), walkthrough video shows complete workflow, connects to Shibuya + Peregrine testnets

4. **Test Coverage:**  
   CI pipeline green, `npm run test:all` passes, ≥70% coverage on contracts and KILT module (measured with cargo-tarpaulin and nyc)

5. **Reproducible Documentation:**  
   External reviewer (not on our team) can follow DEPLOYMENT.md and replicate everything, VERIFICATION.md includes all artifacts (contract address, example DIDs/CIDs, transaction hashes), no "TBD" or "TODO" placeholders

6. **Code Quality:**  
   Apache 2.0 LICENSE in all repos, README in each repo, zero compiler warnings (`cargo clippy` clean), zero linter errors (`npm run lint` clean)

7. **Open Source:**  
   All repos public on GitHub, CONTRIBUTING.md present, issue templates configured

