|-------|-------|----------------|
| **1-2** | KILT Integration | Set up KILT SDK, build DID creation module, configure Peregrine testnet, define CType schema for press credentials, test Sporran wallet connection |
| **3-4** | Contract Development | Write ink! publication registry contract, implement signature verification, test locally with Swanky Node, write unit tests |
| **5** | IPFS Integration | Build IPFS upload/retrieval module, configure gateway failovers (Infura, Pinata, Cloudflare), integration tests combining KILT + IPFS |
